Package de.saxsys.mvvmfx.utils.mapping.accessorfunctions Description

This package contains functional interfaces to define accessors of different types. These are used to define a mapping with the ModelWrapper. We need these explicit interfaces to support Java with the type deduction when using method references of the getter/setter methods of the mapped model class.
Author:
manuel.mauky
